---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html
>
  <Header title="MLOps Workflow" />
  <body>
    <div class="content" style="display: flex;">
  <!-- Left column: Professional profile, styles preserved -->
      <aside style="width: 370px; min-width: 370px; color: #fff; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2.5rem 3rem; margin-right: 3rem;">
  <!-- Profile image -->
        <img src="./assets/profile.png" alt="Esteban Ramirez" style="width: 240px; height: 240px; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 1rem; border: 2px solid #fff; display: block;">
  <!-- Name -->
        <h2 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; font-size: 2rem; text-align: left; white-space: nowrap;">Esteban Ramirez</h2>
  <!-- Position -->
        <div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: left;">Data Science</div>
  <!-- Contact buttons -->
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/esteban-rm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="button w-button">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.761 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.239-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-10h3v10zm-1.5-11.268c-.966 0-1.75-.784-1.75-1.75s.784-1.75 1.75-1.75 1.75.784 1.75 1.75-.784 1.75-1.75 1.75zm13.5 11.268h-3v-5.604c0-1.337-.026-3.063-1.868-3.063-1.868 0-2.154 1.459-2.154 2.967v5.7h-3v-10h2.881v1.367h.041c.401-.761 1.379-1.563 2.841-1.563 3.039 0 3.602 2.002 3.602 4.604v5.592z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Est3banR" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="button w-button">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.757-1.333-1.757-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.84 1.236 1.84 1.236 1.07 1.834 2.809 1.304 3.495.997.108-.775.418-1.305.762-1.605-2.665-.305-5.466-1.334-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.523.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23a11.52 11.52 0 013.003-.404c1.018.005 2.045.138 3.003.404 2.291-1.553 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.873.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.803 5.624-5.475 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .322.218.694.825.576C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/>
            </svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
  <!-- Random text -->
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #ccc; text-align: justify; width: 260px;">
          Profesional creativo y analítico, apasionado por descubrir patrones en datos y construir soluciones inteligentes. Siempre buscando nuevos retos y oportunidades para crecer.
        </p>
      </aside>
  <!-- Right column: Main landing -->
      <nav class="main" style="flex: 1; padding: 2rem;">
        <div class="container">
          <main class="fold-content-container">
            <div class="fold-content">
              <div style="position: relative;">
                <a href="/" style="position: absolute; left: -8rem; top: 25px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.5rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" style="margin-right:8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M15.5 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
                  </svg>
                  Back
                </a>
                <h1 style="margin: 0;">MLOps Workflow</h1>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Single project cell -->
            <div style="background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #eee; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 2rem; height: 270px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
              <div style="flex: 1 1 auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                <img src="./assets/mlops-project.jpg" alt="MLOps Workflow" style="position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
              </div>
              <div class="chips-container chips-container-small-width" style="padding: 0.6rem;">
                <div class="single-chip small-chip">Python</div>
                <div class="single-chip small-chip">Docker</div>
                <div class="single-chip small-chip">AWS</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Project description -->
            <div style="margin-top: 2rem; color: #fff; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;">
              Este workflow de MLOps integra herramientas modernas para el desarrollo, despliegue y monitoreo de modelos de machine learning. Permite automatizar procesos, mejorar la reproducibilidad y escalar soluciones en la nube.
            </div>

            <!-- Project URL -->
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
              <span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #fff;">URL del proyecto:</span>
              <div style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                <a href="https://github.com/Est3banR/proyecto_mlops" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #0077cc; font-size: 1rem; word-break: break-all;">https://github.com/Est3banR/proyecto_mlops</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </main>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
